    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――全国ツアー中のある日",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_02-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "今日泊まる宿は温泉旅館なんですね",
      "startTime": 2.2333333174,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ツアー中は毎日忙しいから\n今夜くらいは温泉で英気を養ってくれ",
      "startTime": 8.4999999682,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_02-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます\nさくらも修学旅行みたいだってはしゃいでました",
      "startTime": 13.5333333651,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "他のメンバーの部屋に行くのは構わないが\n夜更かしはしないようにな。明日も予定があるだろ？",
      "startTime": 20.4333352088,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_02-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "はい、例のサプライズ企画で\n以前話したファンの恋愛相談に乗ってきます",
      "startTime": 27.9666667302,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_02-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "どうアドバイスするか自分なりに考えてみましたが……\n今後のこともあるので、少し不安ですね",
      "startTime": 36.6723108013,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "今後って、どういうことだ？",
      "startTime": 40.6666684944,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_02-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "実は、ファンレターで私に恋愛相談してきたファンは\n一人だけじゃないんです",
      "startTime": 48.4000020662,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_02-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "今回のツアー中、私は三人の恋愛相談に\n乗ることになっていて……",
      "startTime": 54.1000020662,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_02-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "一人目でこんなに苦戦していて、全員にちゃんと\nアドバイス出来るのか……今から気が重いです",
      "startTime": 59.4309739246,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_02-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "どうすれば、もっと上手に\n恋のアドバイスが出来るようになるんでしょう……",
      "startTime": 66.9204420483,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_02-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……\n短期間で恋愛のプロになれる方法はありませんか？",
      "startTime": 71.8412926022,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "短期間でと言われても……そういうのは\n沢山恋愛をして経験を積むしかないんじゃないか？",
      "startTime": 80.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_02-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "経験を積む……\nだったら、明日までに恋愛経験を沢山積めば……",
      "startTime": 87.3911509671,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_02-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんも\n今夜はこの旅館に泊まるんですよね？",
      "startTime": 93.7190593106,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_02-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "この後、お部屋に行ってもいいですか？\n私が恋愛経験を積むのに協力して下さい！",
      "startTime": 99.9666672069,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_02-rei013.m4a",
      "text": "ここが{user}さんの\n泊まってる部屋なんですね",
      "startTime": 107.4000068268,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "怜……。恋愛経験を積むのに協力してほしいって\nどういうことだ？",
      "startTime": 114.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_02-rei014.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね……では、早速始めましょう\n{user}さん……",
      "startTime": 121.5666728018,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_02-rei015.m4a",
      "text": "……ノートパソコンを貸して下さい",
      "startTime": 123.1666656968,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ノートパソコン？\n確かに持ってきてはいるが……",
      "startTime": 127.866665999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_02-rei016.m4a",
      "text": "それを使ってサブスクで映画を観ます。徹夜で",
      "startTime": 130.6999837713,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "恋愛映画を観まくるので、朝まで付き合って下さい",
      "startTime": 135.2666641871,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "恋愛経験を積むってそういう意味か……",
      "startTime": 139.366650438,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "それなら一人で観た方が集中出来るんじゃないか？\nパソコンは貸すから、自分の部屋で……",
      "startTime": 146.6333326656,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_02-rei017.m4a",
      "text": "私の寝起きの悪さは知ってますよね？\n朝まで起きられない自信があります！",
      "startTime": 155.6019564847,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "もしも夜中に寝落ちしたら",
      "startTime": 153.4233216665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_02-rei018.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんは私が眠らないように\nそばにいて見張っていて下さい",
      "startTime": 160.8666549998,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_keytap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4900.011666899985,
          "startTime": 165.7666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_02-rei019.m4a",
      "text": "では早速、配信サイトを開いて……\nうーん……恋愛映画って数が多いですね……",
      "startTime": 169.7141955532,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
